data.description: Location, location, location! This single-story home in Garden Lakes boasts a swimming pool and split floor plan with neutral finishes. The kitchen features new stainless-steel appliances, granite countertops, and a unique island.  With a master suite, 3 bedrooms, a separate office, and a 3-car garage, there's space for everyone!  Enjoy the owned solar, low maintenance backyard with artificial grass, and large covered patio. Take advantage of Garden Lakes' parks, fishing, and amenities. Plus, it's conveniently close to freeways, Glendale's entertainment district, and Cardinal Stadium. Don't miss out on this gem!
